node.text: I really, very much enjoy this human being. She’s a fuckin boss and she gave me a dope af charcuterie board one time. She also gave me a lot of confidence to be an absolute weirdo in front of her. ❤️❤️ @melissamccarthy @9strangershulu that last photo was taken by @mannyjacinto ❤️

node.text: The first day on 9 Perfect Strangers when no one recognised me, not even my iPhone. @morereginahall took the longest to realise it was me. 😂Thank you to @sianhowardmakeup & @chrissyzemura for transforming meee! I still have the fake teeth if anyone wants to borrow them for Halloween. 🦑 @9strangershulu @melvingregg
